OR NOT?

00:19:30,670 --> 00:19:33,072
YES, I GOT ALL THE PATENTS.

00:19:33,072 --> 00:19:35,074
SO, DAN, YOU'RE THE ONLY GUY
IN THE WORLD

00:19:35,074 --> 00:19:38,210
