THEN I KILL YOU.

00:20:30,863 --> 00:20:32,398
(laughs)

00:20:32,398 --> 00:20:35,501
HOW MUCH DO YOU HAVE,
PERSONALLY, INTO THIS BUSINESS?

00:20:35,501 --> 00:20:38,404
I PROBABLY HAVE ABOUT
$400,000 OR $500,000‐‐
WHOA.

00:20:38,404 --> 00:20:41,240
DAN, DANIEL, PLEASE STOP. IT'S
PAINFUL FOR ME TO HEAR THIS.

00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:43,409
YOU KNOW WHAT BUSINESS
YOU OUGHT TO BE IN?

00:20:43,409 --> 00:20:45,644
THE RESEARCH BUSINESS.
YOU ARE SO GOOD AT IT.

00:20:45,644 --> 00:20:47,646
YOU'VE BEEN RESEARCHING
THIS THING TO DEATH,

00:20:47,646 --> 00:20:49,181
AND YOU MISSED THE MARK.

00:20:49,181 --> 00:20:51,884
YOU DON'T HAVE AN ORDER.

00:20:51,884 --> 00:20:53,753
