COVERPLAY IS THE FIRST
AND ONLY...

00:31:58,417 --> 00:32:00,786
SLIPCOVER FOR PLAY YARDS.

00:32:00,786 --> 00:32:02,754
SO YOU BRING THAT WITH YOU
WHEREVER YOU GO?

00:32:02,754 --> 00:32:04,623
IS THAT THE IDEA?

00:32:04,623 --> 00:32:07,726
